{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1834980/extras/partygames.gif?t=1732128657\" /><br>Hang out in 4-8 player online multiplayer lobbies with your friends or randoms who will soon become your friends. Join the party for one common goal: <strong>SUMMON CTHULHU</strong>.<br>At least\u2026 if you are a monster.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Deceive Your Friends</strong></h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1834980/extras/humanstuff.gif?t=1732128657\" /><br>To the few human operatives out there: this is your time to shine. Be an absolute menace: lie, sabotage, do everything you can to cause chaos! Remember: friends are temporary, stealing ritual fluid to make magical spells for profit - that is forever.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Second Chances</strong></h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1834980/extras/secondchances.gif?t=1732128657\" /><br>\u201c<i>But guys, I\u2019m terrible at social deduction games\u2026</i>\u201d<br>Worry not, noob! Set your skill issue aside for there\u2019s always a second chance in Ritual Night! Without early eliminations, the gameplay becomes more watchable and fun for everyone throughout!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Refined Chaos</strong></h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1834980/extras/sacrifice.gif?t=1732128657\" /><br>Randomness and chaos being core, hidden roles are encouraged to create chaos and cause confusion instead of preventing information from leaking.<br><br>Nothing in the game is a direct tell or leak of key information on who the imposter may be. Even if one imposter gets found out early in the game, the tools at their disposal are designed around the potential for causing maximum chaos to muddle that information.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Roguelite, Upgrades, Emergence</strong></h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1834980/extras/upgrades.gif?t=1732128657\" /><br>Roguelite elements such as procedurally generated props that spawns into the map or additional abilities given to the players as a consequence of their actions.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>He's coming...</strong></h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1834980/extras/lore.gif?t=1732128657\" /><br>Join the effort of dominating regions deeply connected to the unfathomable horror that is about to unfold. Uncover secrets, ciphers, and lore that will one day all make sense.<br><br>Until then? Enjoy the Party.","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Barista of the Month","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1834980/d850d7eab8b524330805b94733020ad918c25e2b.jpg"},{"name":"Playing With Fire","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1834980/e9a28753479e89be49d70c18069d3c73927be754.jpg"},{"name":"Arsonist","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1834980/80c72119d10956db1224133b7bd51cc45a5be2b6.jpg"},{"name":"Cthugha","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1834980/0b5e6c6fe2e06b0c959b9bbfd71dae31182cdce4.jpg"},{"name":"Cardboard Castles","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1834980/1900d882ad23b3b52606a7730c990448e61eea18.jpg"},{"name":"Safe Space","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1834980/32d1fd39cd9baf25a75aba29cc309ae6b3ef01a6.jpg"},{"name":"Solid Snake","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1834980/90570677ce3bee003cb4606abe2a4f3c3824edcb.jpg"},{"name":"Initiation","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1834980/efd40a5e6371750dc6bd49463a67445be050ad9